5/5  rDev +12.4%look: 5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 5The beer comes in a rich intense hazy orange color, straight nectarine juice.
The aroma explodes of fresh passionfruit, mango, juicy peach, starfruit, a bit of bready sweetness, with dank and earthy pine.
The flavor follows with passionfruit juice. This beer is hugely juicy. Onto sweet mango, juicy peach, tangerine, orange, touches of melon and lychee, with a white bready malt in the middle, then the beer turns onto an intense dank and pine needle quality with medium bitterness.
Simply one of the best DIPAs I've had. 525 charactersdar482, Sep 25, 2015
